# Reproducible data artifacts. data/heat.duckdb IS tracked (the dashboard and the
# CI static-site build read it); only caches and throwaway plots are ignored.
/data/cache/
/data/*.png

# The static site is built in CI (dashdown build dashboard --out site) so the
